gino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tOn 14, Aug, the famous actor Wang Baoqiang posted a weibo to annouce the end of his marriage.</p>\n<p>\n\tThis week's topic: Divorce (90-110 words)<br />\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) Share your story of divorce<br />\n\t2) What do you think of divorce ?<br />\n\t3) Is it bad? Why or why not ?<br />\n\t4) Anything you would like to write</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe year when I was enrolled in college is 2010. My foreign teacher, an old wise but funny British gentlemen, once pointed out in his class that one third of Chinese people would divorce in no more than ten years. At that time, I was extremely astonished about the appalling high divorce percentage thus I deduced it to be scaremongering. Unfortunately, numerous clues eventually confirm the correctness. When couples are in a state of Incompatibility, divorce may be the best available option on the table. Cease the confrontation, heal the wounds then embrace a brand-new start.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169732394779/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827527/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827527\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749886/\">英语四级听力：超准！听力5大原则</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p870694/\">你真的不用以此为耻，这9件事再正常不过了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p856860/\">快收下这50个表达心情的常用词 别蓝瘦香菇了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p871671/\">慢半拍的老外终于开始集体吐槽《爵迹》了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857774/\">《生活大爆炸》追剧笔记S10E3：这瓶我请</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p872844/\">手指长短见天赋：你是运动达人还是记忆天才</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844721/\">双语美文：桥下那位流浪汉教会了我什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p8