  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p848360\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tWe start with a man from South Africa whose life was saved by books. Philani Dladla first fell in love with reading when he was a child. But as he grew older his life took a turn for the worse, and he found himself <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/addicted\" target=\"_blank\">addicted</a> to hard drugs and living rough on the streets of Johannesburg. It was his <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/passion\" target=\"_blank\">passion</a> for reading that helped him to turn his life around. He's been telling me his story.</p>\n<p>\n\tMy first ever book was a gift from a man that my mom used to work for. It was my first ever birthday gift. I was 11, turning 12 and he gave me a book about, like politics in South Africa. Obviously I didn't know about what the book was about because I couldn't read or speak English <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/properly\" target=\"_blank\">properly</a>.</p>\n<p>\n\tSo did you set about learning English so you could read it?</p>\n<p>\n\tYeah. I had to spend most time <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/indoors\" target=\"_blank\">indoors</a> by myself. I used a lot of help from a dictionary to just try and understand what other words meant. You can imagine a book about politics for a 11-year-old. It was just like a very big challenge.</p>\n<p>\n\tWhat did he say about you reading it? What conditions that he puts on it?</p>\n<p>\n\tThat if I was to read it and tell him what it was about, he was gonna give me more books. I used to go, visit him almost every weekend. On his will, he left me like 500 of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/collectible\" target=\"_blank\">collectible</a> books which I still have today.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p848360/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p848360\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p749886/\">英语四级听力：超准！听力5大原则</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p870694/\">你真的不用以此为耻，这9件事再正常不过了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p856860/\">快收下这50个表达心情的常用词 别蓝瘦香菇了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p871671/\">慢半拍的老外终于开始集体吐槽《爵迹》了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857774/\">《生活大爆炸》追剧笔记S10E3：这瓶我请</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p872844/\">手指长短见天赋：你是运动达人还是记忆天才</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844721/\">双语美文：桥下那位流浪汉教会了我什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p857798/\">今秋最值得学的10门英语课程</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p874583/\">《爸爸去哪儿4》：去哪找阿拉蕾这么萌的娃啊</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768445/\">有声美文：你们的恋爱关系健康吗？</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.c